parameter.value: I was also affected by the time of violence

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: when they were doing the operations to sterilize people.

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: by saying we were going to be OK,

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: that we couldn’t have any more family,

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: that our families were too big already

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: and we wouldn’t be able to support them in the future.

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: I was sterilized when I was 25 years of age.

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: I could end up with more than a dozen children..

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: ‘Where are you going to leave such a big family?’

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: that said that we had to have the operation.

parameter.name: Text

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: Then we… In my case I said no,

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: because our work here in the countryside is hard,

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: that we live from our fields,

parameter.value: Here in the countryside we carry wood,

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: from our ranch in our saddlebag,

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: and we wouldn’t be able to live like that anymore.

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: that it was just a simple cut,

parameter.value: that it wouldn’t affect us at all,

parameter.value: and that’s how they have convinced us,

parameter.name: Text

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: Asking where we would leave those children in the future,

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: And we said we would think about it,

parameter.value: and the nurses kept looking for us,

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: wherever we were, as if we were delinquents.

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: They even told us to do it without telling our husbands.
